{"id": 1635, "genre": 1000, "title": "关于“吃得更高级”，你看穿了哪些套路？", "description": "用餐时请时刻铭记，吃的不是料理，是职人先生的匠心。（题图来自：J.S. Pughe）", "record_count": 15884, "comment_count": 35, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170418131809Yu57ZeBazS9jA6hE.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-04-19T17:00:01Z", "questions": [{"id": 2167, "title": "关于“吃得更高级”，你看穿了哪些套路？", "content": "关于“吃得更高级”，你看穿了哪些套路？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 193830, "content": "“从农场到餐桌”，工序越简单越好，恨不得直接蹲在田里吃", "image": "img/option/option/20170418131927Mx5vdgtSzCkbFecQ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 193831, "content": "返璞归真，“丑橘”“丑柑”“丑蕉”，越丑越淳朴", "image": "img/option/option/20170418134219iFHQ13R7Ax4Nvprt.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 193838, "content": "食材保质期越短越高级，能呆到下个点的都算不及格", "image": "img/option/option/20170418132628RxfCkdysejiALvb6.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 193837, "content": "设备要炫，噱头要足，干冰要够", "image": "img/option/option/20170418132550LbwoAqyTa6QFPp0N.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 193832, "content": "水果质感要像肉，肉的质感得像水果，总之不要像自己才高级", "image": "img/option/option/20170418132158gyrZf6pPQGLoUdhj.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 193847, "content": "盘子要大，食物分量要小，酱料很重要", "image": "img/option/option/201704181346336Cgm9YwTXjI3kv0R.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 193845, "content": "杯皿盛器要丰富，每种食材都有和它搭档的特别容器", "image": "img/option/option/20170418133814bfkaSFnOl6UuRzWT.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 193840, "content": "肌理打乱重组的分子料理，比如酒石酸葡萄糖多酚重组的龙虾", "image": "img/option/option/20170418133159lfcJes7BYzEKxUZ6.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}